piskvorky_server

  • Classes in piskvorky_server used by piskvorky_server 
    Class and Description
    IStatisticWriter
    interface, that describes manipulation with statistics file, when you want to add there some new results or send it to someone
    Server
    class, that represents server (serversocket), for each connected user there is an instance of private class ClientThread, which handles the communication between server and the client
    Server.ClientThread
    for every connected user, there will be a special thread maintaining a communication with him (listening to his socket)
    StatisticWriter
    class, that implements IStatisticWriter
    StatisticWriter.Result
    private class, that represents the result of all games between two players
